Then Sir Thomas said Like any other rational man , I have occasionally thought of this endeavor at which you hint . 
We exist you and I and all the others in what we glibly call the universe . 
There are no grounds for believing that this particular method of communication is adequate , or even that the agents which produce it are veracious . 
Meanwhile , we are in touch with what exists through our five senses only . 
It may be that they lie to us . 
There is , at least , no reason for assuming them to be infallible . 
