I cannot tell you oh , not even you ! how happy these three years have been with her . 
Eh , well ! the gods are jealous of such happiness . 
You will remember how her mother died ? It appears that Honoria is threatened with a slow consumption , and a death such as her mother's was . 
There was no need to frighten her . 
